Element


bibliomisc
&bibliomisc.purpose;


&bibliomisc.synopsis.gen;
Description



The BiblioMisc element is a wrapper for bibliographic
information that does not fit neatly into the other bibliographic
fields (such as Author and Publisher).


Processing expectations


&format.inline;
It is recommended that the
Role attribute be used to identify the
kind of information that this element contains.



